      <title><![CDATA[An Appeal for African Scouts: Canon William Palmer to Imperial Scout Headquarters, May 5, 1923 [Letter]]]></title>
      <link>https://cyh.rrchnm.org/items/show/98</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<div class="element-set">
